# Tujuan: contoh cron WIB untuk scheduler Hermes phase 1
# Caller: operator VPS saat setup scheduler
# Dependensi: automation/run-telegram-job.sh, jobs/*.md, telegram-config.json
# Main Functions: baseline cron yang aman untuk phase 1
# Side Effects: mengirim prompt scheduler ke topic Telegram

# Hermes scheduler blueprint
# Server timezone assumed: Asia/Jakarta (WIB)
# Uses a separate scheduler bot to post into the same Telegram topics that Hermes watches.
# Requires:
# - automation/telegram-config.json
# - TELEGRAM_RUNNER_ENV or automation/telegram-runner.env
# - automation/run-telegram-job.sh

# Morning brief
0 7 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh morning_brief /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/morning-brief.md updates

# CRM review
0 8 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh crm_review /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/crm-review.md personal-crm

# Security audit
# Phase 1: keep manual until security lane is verified end-to-end.
# 0 9 * * * hermes security audit --deep

# Content nag
0 10 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh content_nag_1 /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/content-nag.md content
0 13 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh content_nag_2 /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/content-nag.md content
0 16 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh content_nag_3 /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/content-nag.md content

# Silent heartbeats every 4 hours during active window
30 10 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh heartbeat_1 /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/heartbeat.md updates
30 14 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh heartbeat_2 /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/heartbeat.md updates
30 18 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh heartbeat_3 /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/heartbeat.md updates
30 22 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh heartbeat_4 /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/heartbeat.md updates

# End of day summary
0 18 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh end_of_day_summary /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/end-of-day-summary.md updates

# Overnight staggered subagents
# Phase 1: manual trigger only.
# 0 1 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh overnight_research /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/overnight-research.md tasks
# 30 1 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh overnight_leads /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/overnight-leads.md personal-crm
# 0 2 * * * /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/run-telegram-job.sh overnight_builder /Users/banirisset/2_Areas/banirisset/automation/jobs/overnight-builder.md tasks
